title: How Much Available Space Does My Phone Provide?
answer:
In the standard configuration, your phone provides 512 MB of RAM, 800 MB of internal  

storage, and a 2.10 GB internal microSD card.  

Because software is installed on your phone, the available space is smaller than that in the  

standard configuration.  

The available space is as follows:  

? RAM: about 300 MB, depending on the software installed on your phone.  

? Internal storage: 800 MB, depending on the software installed on your phone.  

? Internal microSD card: 2.10 GB, depending on the software installed on your phone
